{"tid":1394903,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"台北連儂牆合法了！10議員跨黨派撐香港","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T02:28:30.000Z","uid":296328,"like":339,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ce0e3184c1e8e6c18922a79f0ad9bcf5f68a5c","tid":1394903,"uid":296328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:39:34.000Z","msg":"前幾日，台北鬧區出現2小時後遭拆除，也曾遭遇中國愛國同心會破壞的連儂牆，在今天，由台灣十多名跨黨派台北市議員聯手，出錢出力合法申請地下道使用權，並交由香港邊城青年管理，撐香港之餘，更凸顯台灣民主多元且尊重法治的可貴。<br />\n<br />\n台北市議員「呱吉」邱威傑表示，「民主社會應該要包容多元的聲音」，現在這條台灣大學附近的地下道，「是由台北市議員共同申請的連儂牆，是市民自由表達意見的地方」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bDcU0VX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbDcU0VX.png&h=81f99156&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8aa1f7a57745e320fe449bb11da2a74dcaaf1dcd","tid":1394903,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:45:40.000Z","msg":"【 香港可能面對緊一場極大嘅人道災難 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394867</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"311200411a8e251b6d74c7304edbceec0a009feb","tid":1394903,"uid":184433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:01:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7086287c2280ec63c98041140664c0dcce38bd8e","tid":1394903,"uid":36113,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5509cbab0633c6ef8a2dca3a3f93bcf374fe250","tid":1394903,"uid":126083,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"平時有睇開呱吉嘅片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不可多得嘅好議員嚟，大學綴學之後做到Disney唔記得乜部門嘅manager到依家創業，選議員，質問唔同權力確保check of balance<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港有多幾個好似佢咁嘅議員就好"},{"pid":"d89c930ad5cb181b39e1155aa4464479289a577d","tid":1394903,"uid":84741,"like":0,